# OTA packages (binary files)
*.bin
*.hex
*.elf
src/Diagnostics/OTA/update-packages/*.bin

# Safety and requirements (keep templates, ignore filled)
**/FMEA_filled.xlsx
**/HARA_filled.xlsx
**/requirements_filled.xlsx

# Sensitive data
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
certificates/
secrets/

# Large data files
# NOTE:
# - 전역 무시는 협업 전달 누락을 유발할 수 있어 해제한다.
# - 대용량 산출물은 경로 기반(예: logging/, tmp_rm/)으로 관리한다.

# Python (if using Python tools)
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
*.egg-info/
venv/
.venv/
ENV/

# Node.js (if using Node tools)
node_modules/
npm-debug.log
yarn-error.log

# Compiled documentation
*.aux
*.out
*.toc

# Backup files
*.backup
*.old

# Configuration management
**/baseline-records/*.lock
**/change-requests/*.pending

# Project local stash (do not commit)
tmp_rm/
.codex-tmp/

# Local RAG reference vault (large/local-only)
driving-situation-alert/reference/
driving-situation-alert/tmp/reference-20260305T063406Z-1-001/

nul
